        <Description>perl-Net-DBus-GLib provides an extension to the perl-Net-DBus module allowing integration with the GLib mainloop. To integrate with the main loop, simply get a connection to the bus via the methods in Net::DBus::GLib rather than the usual Net::DBus module. That's it - every other API remains the same.</Description>
